{"tid":538683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天線寶寶「丁丁」逝世 享年52歲","createTime":"2018-01-24T00:01:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-24T00:51:21.000Z","uid":32511,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f7063abea5a7c82825be56aa594750fa06048f08","tid":538683,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T00:01:25.000Z","msg":"兒童節目「天線寶寶」中飾演「丁丁」的男星班拿斯（Simon Shelton Barnes）友人透露<br />\n已於17日去世，享年52歲。<br />\n <br />\n綜合外電報導，班拿斯的友人透露班拿斯於生日後4日（17日）與世長辭，但未說明死因<br />\n。據悉，此角色原定將由演員湯普森（Dave Thompson）飾演，但經嘗試後發現並不適合<br />\n，才由班拿斯挑起大樑，班拿斯從1997年至2001年初版節目結束擔任「天線寶寶」中的「<br />\n丁丁」一角。<br />\n <br />\n根據角色設定，「丁丁」是4位「天線寶寶」中年紀和體型最大一位，常常提著一個紅色<br />\n袋子到處走，愛跳舞但常跌倒。由於角色頭上有個倒三角型天線，加上以紫色為主調，曾<br />\n有保守派人士質疑「丁丁」是同性戀者。班拿斯早年受訪時曾笑言：「丁丁只有3歲啊，<br />\n天真無邪年紀，怎會想這麼多？問這些問題的人，才有問題吧！」他曾把「天線寶寶」比<br />\n喻為電視界的披頭四（Beatles）和接招合唱團（Take That），並表示雖然參演「天線寶<br />\n寶」有風險，但肯定值得一試。<br />\n <br />\n除了「丁丁」之外，班拿斯也曾受過芭蕾舞與編舞家的訓練。班拿斯去世後，其親友亦紛<br />\n紛於社群網站上發文悼念。其中兒子亨利（Henry）寫道：「我在星期三失去了父親。他<br />\n待人溫柔而且體貼入微，我敬愛他多於一切&hellip;&hellip;」班拿斯侄女、英國女演員阿塔克（Emil<br />\ny Jane Atack）亦在悼念文章形容叔叔極具才華、深得身邊每位尊敬：「他離開得多麼突<br />\n然！」"},{"pid":"9144df291dfa78d01684a2a43776bae73cb1fe91","tid":538683,"uid":50457,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T00:06:13.000Z","msg":"Tinky Winky，Dipsy，Laa-Laa, Po...<br />\nTeletubbies...Teletubbies..<br />\nSay Hello!<br />\nHello!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6616ffaa75c3b17121f71cf35abadf34d871c1b6","tid":538683,"uid":32511,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T00:16:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/24/081619_9b5b7203872cb20f65c9c6fdbb4036ff.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F24%2F081619_9b5b7203872cb20f65c9c6fdbb4036ff.png&h=c4734c34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6351fa49810e2e0ffd4dd1730ea72187ba0e71e","tid":538683,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T00:21:15.000Z","msg":"叫天使得得b"},{"pid":"1193ab57e00f873475a49beefb2371b72a8a19cf","tid":538683,"uid":6532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T00:22:04.000Z","msg":"天妒英才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5c357c23c1f1d4200b953b7bfb6e4efd7ab532","tid":538683,"uid":143646,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T00:23:46.000Z","msg":"得罪講句 其實有咩好睇？ 好恐怖"},{"pid":"eae0d855d558781a8628c82fde1bdcca4b8db627","tid":538683,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T00:25:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/joibe/1186851901.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fjoibe%2F1186851901.gif&h=c949dfd2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1ecbff2af6ccd917c499c571f241146dd0dec16","tid":538683,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T00:51:21.000Z","msg":"最肉酸果隻得得b <br />\n得lala可愛"}]}